Package: netseer
Type: Package
Title: Graph Prediction from a Graph Time Series
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Sevvandi", "Kandanaarachchi", email = "sevvandik@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0337-0395")),
  person("Brodie", "Oldfield", 
  role = c("aut") ),
  person("Conrad", "Sanderson", 
  role = c("aut") ),
  )
Maintainer: Sevvandi Kandanaarachchi <sevvandik@gmail.com>
Description: Predicting the structure of a graph (including new nodes and edges)
    from a time series of graphs. An adapted form of Flux Balance Analysis is used
    in conjuction with time series prediction methods to predict the graph structure
    at a future time point.  Details of the underlying algorithm are available in
    Kandanaarachchi et al (2026) <doi:10.1007/978-981-95-4969-6_27>.
